{"tid":684962,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你明知道永遠唔會有轉機","createTime":"2018-05-31T04:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T11:30:16.000Z","uid":135488,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bcf6b7513d5efcdde683d7d7cc5b9a5262aad9b5","tid":684962,"uid":135488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T04:20:00.000Z","msg":"親情 愛情 友情都係<br />\n親情：同屋企人無咩感情 尤其是老豆 每次一齊食飯都好似搭檯咁<br />\n愛情：用情太深 單戀又放唔低<br />\n友情：無遇過知己 最多都只係一班一齊吃喝玩樂打機嘅playmates<br />\n<br />\n我明知所有事都唔會有轉機 但仍然苟且偷生、行屍走肉般殘存 為的只係襯托大家 總要有我哩種不幸嘅人 大家先會感到幸福 祝願天下有情人終成眷屬 唔好一時貪玩背叛愛侶 多啲同親人長輩聯繫下啦 仲有希望同路人唔好灰心啦 以上"},{"pid":"1dba00f04f40f8181eb8d0fc258369e49137ac16","tid":684962,"uid":135488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"連連登都冇人回我 真係無轉機了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43abb801867ca4d45ec49292918f610262a534a9","tid":684962,"uid":54953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T04:50:38.000Z","msg":"we were born to be wasted <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c733dfc6f52e1db3f682c0a54dc03920c882d0a","tid":684962,"uid":37948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T04:55:37.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪有野未講完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623bdcb2789bbde091ad7ea5b9e81639109aae2d","tid":684962,"uid":146299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T05:05:56.000Z","msg":"hi"},{"pid":"4cfcf786dbf65a7279f8d89d1a27cc13632bcf60","tid":684962,"uid":59569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T05:08:12.000Z","msg":"聽緊"},{"pid":"f95139edfadbd45fe1905c9fae9c0cb421ca300f","tid":684962,"uid":135488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43abb801867ca4d45ec49292918f610262a534a9","tid":684962,"uid":5